---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure"
  description="Affiliate and sponsored link disclosure for No Lock-In Printer buying guides and printer comparison tables."
>
  <article class="article">
    <p class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--amber);">Affiliate disclosure</p>
    <h1>Some buying links may earn a commission.</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      No Lock-In Printer may use affiliate or sponsored links to retailers. If you buy through those links, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.
    </p>

    <section class="article-section">
      <h2>How this affects recommendations</h2>
      <p>
        Our recommendations are based on printer lock-in risk, subscription requirements, supply model, Linux or local printing fit, and current research notes. Affiliate availability does not guarantee a recommendation, and non-affiliate products may still be included when they are relevant.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="article-section">
      <h2>Reader responsibility</h2>
      <p>
        Retail prices, availability, cartridge numbers, firmware behavior, and regional driver support can change. Always verify current details with the retailer and manufacturer before purchasing.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</SiteLayout>
